hts and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.332207, "shard": "07", "shelf_id": "sn83020847, 1946-06-27, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/mb", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["newspapers", "springfield (mass.)", "hampden", "springfield", "massachusetts", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["Springfield (Mass.)--Newspapers", "Massachusetts--Springfield", "United States--Massachusetts--Hampden--Springfield"], "subjects": [{"hampden": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hampden&fo=json"}, {"massachusetts": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:massachusetts&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"springfield": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:springfield&fo=json"}, {"springfield (mass.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:springfield+%28mass.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2025-04-13T07:30:49.931Z", "title": "Springfield weekly Republican (Springfield, Mass.), June 27, 1946", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn83020847/1946-06-27/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83020847/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn83020847", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/8e8bcd00-fc32-51bd-bb75-1a84b8c102b1"], "batch": ["mb_basil_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1851", "description": ["Weekly Began in 1851? -123rd year (Sept. 26, 1946). \"Weekly\" appears in masthead ornament. Republican v. 27, no 1397 (June 4, 1851)-v. 31, no 1588 (Feb. 3, 1855) called also Gazette v. 20, no. 23-v. 24, no. 5. Vol. 31, no. 6 (Feb. 10, 1855)-v. 40, no. 52 (Dec. 27, 1872) called also whole no. 1589-2547. Also issued on microfilm from the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service. Arc